notes: 12th Men: PR Reiffel (Aus) and Shahid Nazir (Pak)

AM Stuart claims hattrick in the 12th over of the innings. The batsmen dismissed were: Ijaz Ahmed, Mohammad Wasim and Moin Khan with the 3rd, 4th, and 5th balls of his 6th over. This is the 12th hat-trick in the history of ODIs, and the 2nd by an Australian.
